# Read Master Plan First

**Before doing ANY work in this repo**, read `.cursor/COINWALLET_MASTER_PLAN.md` completely.

That file is the **plan and the loop** — task list, loop status, loop log, and progress all live there.

Then execute **only** the next incomplete task (see **Loop status** at the top) unless the user gave a different explicit instruction for this message.

After completing a task, update the master plan: mark the task ✓, refresh **Loop status**, append to **Loop log**.

Do not skip reading the master plan. Do not start trading AI features. Do not commit unless the user asks.
